---
source: src/core/plan.rs
assertion: plan recommend and explain provide evidence-backed recipe selection
schema:
  recommend: ee.plan.recommend.v1
  explain: ee.plan.explain.v1
contracts:
  - plan recommend matches recipes by task keyword alignment
  - plan recommend returns ranked list with confidence scores
  - plan recommend is deterministic for same task input
  - plan explain returns recipe details with evidence URIs
  - plan explain returns not-found for unknown recipe IDs
  - plan goal redirects to plan recommend
evidence:
  - PlanRecommendReport.recommendations
  - PlanRecommendReport.matchesFound
  - RecipeRecommendation.confidence
  - RecipeRecommendation.matchReasons
  - PlanExplainReport.found
  - PlanExplainReport.steps
